    "This included observations with a verdict such as \"Sarcasm, \" \"Satire, \" or \"unconfirmed.\"",
    "Subsequently, we discarded all languages, that did not have at least 50 observations and languages that did not have at least 10 \"true\" or \"mostly true\" observations.",
    "From the remaining languages, we sampled up to 500 observations.",
    "To compare the ability of our approach across languages, we then used Googletrans, a free python library that utilizes the Google Translate API, to translate all claims from their original language to English.",
    "In this experiment, we compare the performance of GPT-3.5 both with context and without context in English and in the original language."
